{"type": "article", "id": 15792, "title": "BeoLab 90 音响", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-09T07:35:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145855bak89dGExeKWsJZM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦电子品牌 Bang&amp;Olufsen 推出的新款音响 BeoLab 90，号称该品牌史上最高端昂贵的一款。扭曲的外形颇有前卫艺术的风格，在一个房间里放上两个也不嫌重复。音响里面装满了 18 个扬声器，包括七个 AM300-X 高音，七个 AM300-X 中音，三个 Heliox AM1000-1 低音扬声器和一个 Heliox AM1000-1 前置低音单元，实现 360 度环绕声音质。所有扬声器外表都由针织物包裹，搭配实木底座和金属铝，确保高质量的音效。<a href=\"http://www.bang-olufsen.com/en/sound/loudspeakers/beolab-90\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143129wzf0RcBtUV49QjFq.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"855\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.04523227\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143129pJIQVvqY5KidAbaD.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"822\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.00488998\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143130s1bg6iJqj49HSlfW.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"514\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62836186\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}